#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introdución"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kalgebra; has numerous features that allow the user to perform all sorts "
#| "of mathematical operations and show graphically. At one time, this "
#| "program was MathML oriented. Now it can be used by anyone with a little "
#| "mathematical knowledge to solve simple and advanced problems alike."
msgid ""
"&kalgebra; has numerous features that allow the user to perform all sorts of "
"mathematical operations and show graphically. At one time, this program was "
"&MathML; oriented. Now it can be used by anyone with a little mathematical "
"knowledge to solve simple and advanced problems alike."
msgstr ""
"&kalgebra; ten numerosas funcionalidades que permiten realizar todo tipo de "
"operacións matemáticas e mostrar os resultados. En certa altura, este "
"programa estaba orientado cara MathML. Agora calquera o pode utilizar con só "
"uns poucos coñecementos matemáticos para resolver problemas tanto sinxelos "
"como avanzados."

